## Code charts (diagrams) rules

- Diagrams generated by the app must go under **`uploads/flowcharts/`**.
- Each diagram run should generate:
  - a primary diagram text file (`*.flow.txt`) and
  - a human summary (`*.summary.md`).
- Prefer **client-side rendering** (browser) over heavyweight server-side rendering.
- Keep the server “pythonic”: endpoints read files and return HTML/plain text; avoid complex templating.
- Add simple cleanup/versioning later if disk use becomes an issue (keep oldest N).

